FBIS4-6733 "dreas078_d_94005" FBIS-EAS-94-078 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 South Korea Official Leaves for Russia DPRK Loggers Talks Official Leaves for Russia DPRK Loggers Talks SK2104031294 Seoul HANGUK ILBO in Korean 21 Apr 94 p 1 SK2104031294 Seoul HANGUK ILBO Korean BFN [Text] The government urgently sent Choe Tong-chin, first assistant foreign minister, to Russia on 20 April to hold working-level discussions with the Russian Government for the early return of North Korean loggers to the ROK. Assistant Minister Choe will meet with high-ranking authorities of the Russian Foreign Ministry and the Internal Affairs Ministry to confirm the loggers' will to defect and to discuss measures for their security. The ROK Foreign Ministry will form a working-level council headed by Assistant Minister Choe as soon as he returns on 23 April.
